data.description: Location and View all in one!  This home has you going to bed watching the sun set through your windows and waking up to a beautiful sunrise in the morning!  This is Florida living at its finest!  This is a rare find home on the St. Johns River!  This home is situated on the river which goes out ot the intercoastal waterway.  This 4 bedroom/4 bath poolhome is ready for its new owners to enjoy life on the Florida waterway!  Beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, island and custom cabinets, double oven all that overlook the family room and has views of the pool and the river.  Tons of natural light throughout the home, 12' ceilings throughout the home,  A little area with a small beach for wading in the water, and a dock and boat lift to store some of your toys!  This home has 2 garages, one of which was turned into a studio efficiency which can be used to rent out or have a place for your guest to stay.
